SIMPLE: siderealize
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Siderealize
<hw>Si*de"re*al*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To elevate
to the stars, or to the region of the stars; to etherealize.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>German literature transformed, <qex>siderealized</qex>, as we see
it in Goethe, reckons Winckelmann among its initiators.</q> <rj><qau>W.
Pater.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sidereous</ent>⟦br⟧
